    "segment": [
      {
        "text": "In a stunning turn of events, the attack that killed Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei happened in the middle of the morning, catching the regime off guard.",
        "start": 0.16,
        "end": 10.24
      },
      {
        "text": "This wasn't a random strike; it was the result of months of planning.",
        "start": 10.48,
        "end": 14.88
      },
      {
        "text": "President Trump noted that Khamenei was unable to avoid our intelligence and highly sophisticated tracking systems, which allowed the US and Israel to pinpoint his exact location.",
        "start": 15.12,
        "end": 26.08
      },
      {
        "text": "By monitoring the movements of bodyguards and officials, intelligence agencies were able to build up a pattern of life to predict and understand activity, waiting for that perfect moment of vulnerability.",
        "start": 26.24,
        "end": 38.16
      },
      {
        "text": "There was a clear division of labor during the mission, with Israel focusing on strikes to hit leadership targets while the US handled military objectives.",
        "start": 38.32,
        "end": 47.36
      },
      {
        "text": "When the window of opportunity opened, Israeli jets launched a massive assault.",
        "start": 47.6,
        "end": 52.24
      },
      {
        "text": "Reports indicate that they used 30 bombs to attack the compound around 09:40 local time, aiming for an underground bunker.",
        "start": 52.4,
        "end": 61.2
      },
      {
        "text": "The strike was devastating.",
        "start": 61.44,
        "end": 63.2
      },
      {
        "text": "Three senior Iranian defence officials have been confirmed dead by Iran, including the Defence Council secretary and the IRGC commander.",
        "start": 63.44,
        "end": 72.4
      },
      {
        "text": "While this is a massive blow, the future remains uncertain.",
        "start": 72.56,
        "end": 76.32
      },
      {
        "text": "Iran had been prepared for this possibility though, with reports that the plans for succession had already been put in place for its top leadership.",
        "start": 76.64,
        "end": 85.04
      }
    ]
  },
